        public StorageItemChange.Builder<T> changeId(java.lang.String changeId)
        Use a particular ID as the change ID. This value will be used for the next build() call only. After that, the default behavior of using a random UUID will be used.
        Parameters:
        changeId - A string representation of a Java UUID
